@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Parse card text into a Scryfall-like object
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/import-normalization/from-text
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Shivan Dragon {4}{R}{R}\nCreature - Dragon\nFlying\n5/5"
}

### Parse saga abilities
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/import-normalization/saga
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "(As this Saga enters and after your draw step, add a lore counter.)\nI, II - Create a 2/2 token.\nIII - Draw two cards."
}

### Prepare localStorage upload envelope for future persistence
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cards/prepare-localstorage-upload
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientCardKey": "card_123",
  "cardJson": {
    "name": "Test Card",
    "version": "normal"
  },
  "importedCard": {
    "name": "Shivan Dragon",
    "layout": "normal",
    "lang": "en",
    "oracle_text": "Flying",
    "type_line": "Creature - Dragon"
  }
}
